desperado is a 1995 american contemporary western action film written , produced , and directed by robert rodriguez . a sequel to the 1992 film el mariachi , it is the second installment in robert rodriguez 's mexico trilogy . it stars antonio banderas as the mariachi who seeks revenge on the drug lord who killed his lover . the film was screened out of competition at the 1995 cannes film festival . once upon a time in mexico , the final part of the trilogy , was released in 2003 . desperado grossed $ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; million in the united states .